criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Adults (18-60 years of age)

          -  Informed consent

          -  Healthy

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Known history of liver, kidney or hematological disease;

          -  known history of cardiac disease, arrhythmia, QT prolongation;

          -  Autoimmune disorder;

          -  Report of an active infection;

          -  Evidence of G6PD deficiency
